      q: "Acompany that uses the periodic inventory system has the following information regarding its inventory: Description Units Unit price Total January 1 balance 5 $7 $35 Purchase 1 4 9 36 Purchase 2 6 10 60 Purchase 3 3 12 36 Available 18 $167 The company has eight units remaining in inventory at year-end and uses the FIFO method to account for its inventory. What cost of goods sold amount should be reported for its year- end?",
