      q: "Sanni Co. had $150,000 in cash-basis pretax income for the year. At the current year end, accounts receivable decreased by $20,000 and accounts payable increased by $16,000 from their previous year-end balances. Compared to the accrual-basis method of accounting, Sanni's cash-basis pretax income is:",
