      choices: ["Retained earnings, $6,300,000; current-year net income, $1,300,000", "Retained earnings, $6,240,000; current-year net income, $1,300,000", "Retained earnings, $8,240,000; current-year net income, $1,640,000", "Retained earnings, $8,800,000; current-year net income, $1,800,000"],
